SELECT DISTINCT "s1"."gender","s1"."day",SUM("s2"."score_points") AS "total" FROM ("scores" AS "s1") JOIN "scores" AS "s2" WHERE "s1"."gender"="s2"."gender" AND "s2"."day"<="s1"."day" GROUP BY 1,2 ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT "a"."gender","a"."day",SUM("b"."score_points") AS "total" FROM "Scores" AS "a" JOIN "Scores" AS "b" ON "a"."day">="b"."day" AND "a"."gender"="b"."gender" GROUP BY "a"."gender","a"."day" ORDER BY "a"."gender","a"."day"

SELECT "a"."gender","a"."day",SUM("b"."score_points") AS "total" FROM ("Scores" AS "a") JOIN "Scores" AS "b" WHERE "a"."day">="b"."day" AND "a"."gender"="b"."gender" GROUP BY "a"."gender","a"."day" ORDER BY "a"."gender","a"."day"

SELECT "gender","day",SUM("score_points") OVER (PARTITION BY "gender" ORDER BY "gender","day") AS "total" FROM "scores"
